text.tspan: Excess mortality: Deaths from all causes compared to projection based
The percentage difference between the reported number of weekly or monthly deaths in 2020–2024 — broken down by
age group — and the projected number of deaths for the same period based on previous years.
Note: The reported number of deaths might not count all deaths that occurred due to incomplete coverage and delays in reporting.
